        • [ - ] StickandMove - member since 02-Oct-15

          On of the easiest games in the league on paper. For example, the striker named Quekel from De Graafschap played in the second PSV team last year.The only opponent in this game is PSV themselves. If they underestimate their opponent (what they probably will do) they will have a tough night. They can't afford to play anything less then 100 percent. If they are focused only on this game and not already are thinking about the Wolfsburg one on Wednesday they will have a easy night. But one way or another I expect them to concede at least once. I predict 1-3.
